{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "OK, they still working for the OSE but at least-- when were in Chateau Montintin, the demarcation line between the, quote, 'free France' and unoccupied France and occupied France, we were in the unoccupied zone.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That doesn't mean that there weren't any Germans there, because the Germans started coming around even in the unoccupied zones.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they started picking up kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When they got to be 16, the-- kids started disappearing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They had to register with the police, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The function of the OSE actually changed during that period of time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a very open organization before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It started becoming more clandestine, like they tried to-- well, it even got-- they did a lot more later on, after I left.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But what they tried to do is they tried to get the kids out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because they recognized that the-- that the-- the danger were the Jewish kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And in France, the French government, of course, didn't help any, because the French government was really-- they turned over the Jews before the-- even the Germans asked for them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the first ones that turned over is the, quote, 'the foreign Jews,' which include, of course, our group of kids of German, and Austrians, and Belgians, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So those kids were in the most imminent danger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Montintin, yeah?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because once I got to Montintin, I was able to write to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, while I was in Montintin, one of the letters I got from my parents was that had been-- they had moved to a different address in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which, at the time, I recognized that basically they were kicked out and put into a sort of-- they had to sublet a room in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And shortly thereafter, they were deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
